  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 180°C.",
    "Chop onions and mince garlic.",
    "Heat olive oil in a pan, add onions and sauté until translucent.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Stir in cumin, lemon zest, salt, kidney beans, sun-dried tomatoes, and enough water to cover the mixture (about 100ml).",
    "Transfer the mixture into a blender and blend until smooth.",
    "Pour blended mixture back into pan and add more olive oil if needed.",
    "Roast in the oven for 25 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Serve hot as a quiche, cut into wedges."
